{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843591640,"sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","part":{"id":"prt_d7886c1c4001qu8kt0a5ZjHiLe","messageID":"msg_d7886a03a001nK7OtPxp2Df7BZ","sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_999f5850f4b8466b9607fe6c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-017/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n2: \n3: **Module:** pkg/picod\n4: **Language:** Go\n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 目的\n8: \n9: <!-- TODO: Describe the purpose of this change -->\n10: \n11: ## 范围\n12: \n13: ### 包含\n14: <!-- TODO: List what is in scope -->\n15: \n16: ### 不包含\n17: <!-- TODO: List what is out of scope -->\n18: \n19: ## 架构概要\n20: \n21: <!-- TODO: Describe the architecture -->\n22: \n23: ## 影响分析\n24: \n25: ### 直接影响\n26: <!-- TODO: List directly affected components -->\n27: \n28: ### 上游依赖\n29: <!-- TODO: List upstream dependencies -->\n30: \n31: ### 下游依赖\n32: <!-- TODO: List downstream dependents -->\n33: \n34: ### 风险评估\n35: <!-- TODO: List risks and mitigations -->\n36: \n37: ## 备选方案\n38: \n39: <!-- TODO: Document alternatives considered -->\n40: \n41: ## 实现要点\n42: \n43: <!-- TODO: Key implementation details -->\n44: \n45: ## 验收标准\n46: \n47: <!-- TODO: Acceptance criteria -->\n48: \n49: ## 状态\n50: \n51: - [ ] 提案审查\n52: - [ ] 实现\n53: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 53 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-017 — PicoD JWT 中间件\n\n**Module:** pkg/picod\n**Language:** Go\n**Size:** S\n\n## 目的\n\n<!-- TODO: Describe the purpose of this change -->\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n<!-- TODO: List what is in scope -->\n\n### 不包含\n<!-- TODO: List what is out of scope -->\n\n## 架构概要\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-c