{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843592743,"sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","part":{"id":"prt_d7886c68f001Wf2BBQ2bDTaK3g","messageID":"msg_d7886a03a001nK7OtPxp2Df7BZ","sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ab1a1babe75848a5b59f3a67","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 AgentCube Router 添加完整的 JWT 认证与签发能力，实现双向安全通信：\n6: \n7: 1. **入站认证（Inbound Authentication）**：Router 自身的 API 端点需要验证调用方身份，防止未授权访问。当前 Router 的所有 `/v1` 路由均无认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用 sandbox 资源。\n8: 2. **出站签发（Outbound Signing）**：Router 向下游 Sandbox/PicoD 转发请求时，签发 JWT 作为服务间身份凭证，确保下游服务能验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例。\n9: \n10: 现有代码已实现出站签发（`jwt.go` + `proxy.go` 中的 token 注入），但缺失入站认证。本 AR 补全认证链路，满足 `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` 中定义的 `AuthMiddleware` 测试用例（Test-RT-1: 无效 JWT 返回 401，Test-RT-2: 过期 JWT 返回 \"Token Expired\"）。\n11: \n12: ## Scope\n13: \n14: ### In Scope\n15: \n16: 1. **AuthMiddleware 实现**\n17:    - 新增 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法，验证请求 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 头\n18:    - 使用 RSA 公钥验证 RS256 签名（拒绝 HMAC 等弱签名算法）\n19:    - 强制校验 `exp`（过期时间）和 `iat`（签发时间）claim\n20:    - 配置 1 分钟时钟容差（leeway），容忍分布式系统中的时钟偏移\n21:    - 验证失败返回标准化 401 响应：`{\"error\": \"<message>\", \"code\": \"<error_code>\"}`\n22: \n23: 2. **JWTManager 扩展**\n24:    - 在现有 `JWTManager` 上增加 `PublicKey()` 方法，供认证中间件获取验证用的公钥\n25:    - 新增 `ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString string) (*jwt.Token, error)` 方法用于验证入站 token\n26:    - 复用已有的 K8s Secret 密钥持久化机制（`picod-router-identity`），无需新建密钥存储\n27:    - 非集群环境下使用临时密钥对（与现有行为一致，记录 warning 日志）\n28: \n29: 3. **路由保护**\n30:    - 将 `AuthMiddleware` 应用于 `/v1` 路由组（与现有 `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware` 同级）\n31:    - 健康检查端点（`/health/live`、`/health/ready`）保持公开，不受认证保护\n32:    - 中间件顺序：`gin.Logger()` → `gin.Recovery()` → `AuthMiddleware()` → `ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware()`\n33: \n34: 4. **单元测试**\n35:    - 有效 JWT 请求正常放行（200）\n36:    - 无效签名 JWT 返回 401（Test-RT-1）\n37:    - 过期 JWT 返回 401 且错误信息包含 \"Token Expired\"（Test-RT-2）\n38:    - 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401\n39:    - 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n40:    - HMAC 签名（如 HS256）被拒绝，返回 401\n41: \n42: ### Out of Scope\n43: \n44: - 客户端 SDK 的 JWT 获取逻辑（由其他 AR 覆盖）\n45: - RBAC / 基于角色的权限控制（仅做身份验证，不做授权）\n46: - JWT 刷新 / 续期机制（当前 5 分钟有效期由调用方自行管理）\n47: - PicoD 端的认证逻辑变更（已有完整实现，无需修改）\n48: - WorkloadManager 的 Bearer Token 提取逻辑（独立流程，不受影响）\n49: \n50: ## Impact Analysis\n51: \n52: ### Dependencies\n53: \n54: | 依赖 | 用途 | 影响 |\n55: |------|------|------|\n56: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` (v5.2.1) | JWT 签名验证（RS256） | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n57: | `crypto/rsa` | RSA 公钥验证 | Go 标准库，无新增 |\n58: | `pkg/router/jwt.go` | JWTManager 扩展 | 修改现有文件，增加验证方法 |\n59: | `k8s.io/client-go` (v0.34.1) | 密钥 Secret 管理 | 已有依赖，无新增 |\n60: \n61: ### Affected Components\n62: \n63: - **pkg/router/jwt.go**: 增加 `PublicKey()` 和 `ParseAndValidateToken()` 方法\n64: - **pkg/router/middleware.go**: 新增 `AuthMiddleware(jwtManager *JWTManager) gin.HandlerFunc`\n65: - **pkg/router/server.go**: 在 `/v1` 路由组注册 `AuthMiddleware`\n66: - **pkg/router/jwt_test.go** (新增): JWTManager 单元测试\n67: - **pkg/router/middleware_test.go** (新增): AuthMiddleware 单元测试\n68: \n69: ### Risk Assessment\n70: \n71: | 风险 | 等级 | 缓解措施 |\n72: |------|------|----------|\n73: | 启用认证后现有无认证调用方收到 401 | 高 | 文档明确说明向后不兼容变更；提供配置开关可选禁用 |\n74: | RSA 验证延迟影响 Router 吞吐 | 低 | RS256 验证约 0.1-0.3ms/次，对整体延迟影响可忽略 |\n75: | 密钥轮换导致 token 验证失败 | 中 | 密钥持久化到 K8s Secret，重启后复用；轮换需同步更新调用方 |\n76: | 非集群环境下临时密钥重启后变更 | 中 | 记录 warning 日志；生产环境应在集群内运行 |\n77: \n78: ### 与现有组件的交互\n79: \n80: | 组件 | 交互方式 | 影响 |\n81: |------|----------|------|\n82: | PicoD | 共享同一密钥对（Router 存储，PicoD 通过 env var 获取公钥） | 无影响。PicoD 验证 Router 签发的 token，Router 验证客户端发来的 token |\n83: | WorkloadManager | 从 Secret 读取公钥注入 PicoD | 无影响。WorkloadManager 的 Bearer Token 提取逻辑独立 |\n84: | client-go | 生成的 Kubernetes 客户端库 | 无影响。client-go 仅用于 CRD 操作，不涉及 Router API 调用 |\n85: | Session Manager | 创建 sandbox 时调用 WorkloadManager | 无影响。使用 K8s Service Account Token，不经过 Router JWT 体系 |\n86: \n87: ## Alternatives Considered\n88: \n89: ### 1. 复用 PicoD AuthManager 模式（✅ 选定方案）\n90: \n91: **做法**：在 Router 的 `JWTManager` 上增加 token 验证方法，新建 `AuthMiddleware`，模式与 PicoD 的 `AuthManager.AuthMiddleware()` 保持一致。\n92: \n93: **优点**：\n94: - 代码模式统一，降低维护成本\n95: - 复用已有的密钥管理基础设施（K8s Secret）\n96: - 与 PicoD 使用相同的验证参数（RS256、1 分钟 leeway、强制 exp/iat）\n97: - 实现简单，改动集中在 2-3 个文件\n98: \n99: **缺点**：\n100: - Router 和 PicoD 验证的是不同来源的 token（客户端 vs Router），若未来需要区分 token 用途需增加 `aud` claim\n101: \n102: **决策**：采用。与现有架构最契合，满足 TDD manifest 要求，变更范围可控（M 级）。\n103: \n104: ### 2. 引入独立的 OIDC Provider\n105: \n106: **做法**：集成外部 OIDC Provider（如 Dex、Keycloak），Router 作为 OAuth2 Resource Server 验证 access_token。\n107: \n108: **优点**：标准化认证流程，支持多租户，天然支持 token 刷新/吊销/审计  \n109: **缺点**：引入外部依赖，增加部署复杂度，超出 M 级变更范围  \n110: **决策**：不采用。AgentCube 当前为集群内服务，OIDC 的复杂度收益不高。\n111: \n112: ### 3. API Key 认证\n113: \n114: **做法**：使用静态 API Key（通过 header 或 query param 传递），在 Router 配置中维护允许调用方列表。\n115: \n116: **优点**：实现最简单，无加密开销  \n117: **缺点**：密钥轮换困难，无法携带结构化 claim，安全性低于 JWT  \n118: **决策**：不采用。与现有 JWT 体系不兼容，PicoD 端需额外改造。\n119: \n120: ### 4. mTLS 双向认证\n121: \n122: **做法**：Router 启用 mTLS，调用方需提供合法客户端证书。\n123: \n124: **优点**：传输层安全，最高安全级别  \n125: **缺点**：证书管理复杂度高，与现有 JWT 体系重复建设  \n126: **决策**：不采用。可在应用层认证之上叠加，无需推翻重来。\n127: \n128: ## Implementation Notes\n129: \n130: ### AuthMiddleware 错误响应格式\n131: \n132: 与 PicoD 保持一致的 JSON 错误格式：\n133: \n134: ```json\n135: {\n136:   \"error\": \"<human-readable message>\",\n137:   \"code\": \"<machine-readable error code>\"\n138: }\n139: ```\n140: \n141: 错误码定义：\n142: - `UNAUTHORIZED` — 缺少或格式错误的 Authorization 头\n143: - `INVALID_TOKEN` — token 签名无效或格式错误\n144: - `TOKEN_EXPIRED` — token 已过期（错误消息包含 \"Token Expired\"）\n145: - `UNSUPPORTED_SIGNING_METHOD` — 使用了非 RSA 签名算法\n146: \n147: ### 密钥管理\n148: \n149: - 复用现有 `picod-router-identity` Secret\n150: - Router 启动时：尝试创建 Secret（首次）或加载已有密钥对\n151: - 非集群环境：使用临时密钥对（warning 日志），认证功能可用但重启后密钥变更\n152: - 公钥可通过 `JWTManager.PublicKey()` 获取，用于 future 的公钥分发接口\n153: \n154: ### 中间件注册\n155: \n156: ```go\n157: v1 := s.engine.Group(\"/v1\")\n158: v1.Use(gin.Logger())\n159: v1.Use(gin.Recovery())\n160: if s.jwtManager != nil {\n161:     v1.Use(AuthMiddleware(s.jwtManager))\n162: }\n163: v1.Use(ConcurrencyLimitMiddleware(s.config.MaxConcurrentRequests))\n164: ```\n165: \n166: 当 `jwtManager` 为 nil（极端异常情况）时跳过认证中间件，避免 Router 完全不可用。\n167: \n168: ### JWTManager 扩展方法签名\n169: \n170: ```go\n171: // PublicKey 返回用于验证 token 的 RSA 公钥\n172: func (m *JWTManager) PublicKey() *rsa.PublicKey\n173: \n174: // ParseAndValidateToken 验证入站 JWT token\n175: func (m *JWTManager) ParseAndValidateToken(tokenString string) (*jwt.Token, error)\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ### 目录结构\n179: \n180: ```\n181: pkg/router/\n182: ├── jwt.go               # JWTManager（扩展：增加验证方法）\n183: ├── middleware.go        # 中间件（新增 AuthMiddleware）\n184: ├── server.go            # Server（注册 AuthMiddleware）\n185: ├── jwt_test.go          # JWTManager 单元测试（新增）\n186: └── middleware_test.go   # AuthMiddleware 单元测试（新增）\n187: ```\n188: \n189: ## Acceptance Criteria\n190: \n191: 1. **认证中间件**\n192:    - [ ] `AuthMiddleware` 正确验证有效 JWT 并放行请求\n193:    - [ ] 无效签名 JWT 返回 401 `{\"error\": \"...\", \"code\": \"INVALID_TOKEN\"}`\n194:    - [ ] 过期 JWT 返回 401 且错误消息包含 \"Token Expired\"\n195:    - [ ] 缺少 Authorization 头返回 401 `{\"error\": \"...\", \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\"}`\n196:    - [ ] 非 Bearer 类型 token 返回 401\n197:    - [ ] HMAC 签名（HS256）被拒绝，返回 401 `{\"error\": \"...\", \"code\": \"UNSUPPORTED_SIGNING_METHOD\"}`\n198: \n199: 2. **JWTManager 扩展**\n200:    - [ ] `PublicKey()` 返回正确的 RSA 公钥\n201:    - [ ] `ParseAndValidateToken()` 正确验证 RS256 签名\n202:    - [ ] 强制要求 `exp` 和 `iat` claim\n203:    - [ ] 1 分钟时钟容差生效\n204: \n205: 3. **路由集成**\n206:    - [ ] `/v1` 路由组受 AuthMiddleware 保护\n207:    - [ ] `/health/live` 和 `/health/ready` 保持公开\n208:    - [ ] jwtManager 为 nil 时跳过认证（降级）\n209: \n210: 4. **测试覆盖**\n211:    - [ ] 通过 TDD manifest 中 Test-RT-1 和 Test-RT-2\n212:    - [ ] 所有新增代码行覆盖率达到 80% 以上\n213: \n214: ## Status\n215: \n216: - [ ] 提案审查\n217: - [ ] 实现\n218: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 218 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011: Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube Router 添加完整的 JWT 认证与签发能力，实现双向安全通信：\n\n1. **入站认证（Inbound Authentication）**：Router 自身的 API 端点需要验证调用方身份，防止未授权访问。当前 Router 的所有 `/v1` 路由均无认证保护，任何网络可达的客户端均可直接调用 sandbox 资源。\n2. **出站签发（Outbound Signing）**：Router 向下游 Sandbox/PicoD 转发请求时，签发 JWT 作为服务间身份凭证，确保下游服务能验证请求来源为合法的 Router 实例。\n\n现有代码已实现出站签发（`jwt.go` + `proxy.go` 中的 token 注入），但缺失入站认证。本 AR 补全认证链路，满足 `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` 中定义的 `AuthMiddleware` 测试用例（Test-RT-1: 无效 JWT 返回 401，Test-RT-2: 过期 JWT 返回 \"Token Expired\"）。\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **AuthMiddleware 实现**\n   - 新增 `AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc` 方法，验证请求 `Authorization: Bearer <token>` 头\n   - 使用 RSA 公钥验证 RS256 签名（拒绝 HMAC 等弱签名算法）\n   - 强制校验 `exp`（过期时间）和 `iat`（签发时间）claim\n   - 配置 1 分钟时钟容差（leeway），容忍分布式系统中的时钟偏移","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775843592735,"end":1775843592741}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843593889,"sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","part":{"id":"prt_d7886caa1001orgcOGqtM2pZyt","messageID":"msg_d7886a03a001nK7OtPxp2Df7BZ","sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_b5a012c82530482b9b6356ea","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/auth.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/auth.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package picod\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"crypto/rsa\"\n5: \t\"crypto/x509\"\n6: \t\"encoding/pem\"\n7: \t\"fmt\"\n8: \t\"net/http\"\n9: \t\"os\"\n10: \t\"strings\"\n11: \t\"sync\"\n12: \t\"time\"\n13: \n14: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n15: \t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n16: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n17: )\n18: \n19: type AuthManager struct {\n20: \tpublicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n21: \tmutex     sync.RWMutex\n22: }\n23: \n24: func (am *AuthManager) LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error {\n25: \tkeyData := os.Getenv(PublicKeyEnvVar)\n26: \tif keyData == \"\" {\n27: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"environment variable %s is not set\", PublicKeyEnvVar)\n28: \t}\n29: \n30: \tblock, _ := pem.Decode([]byte(keyData))\n31: \tif block == nil {\n32: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"failed to decode PEM block\")\n33: \t}\n34: \n35: \tpub, err := x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey(block.Bytes)\n36: \tif err != nil {\n37: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse public key: %w\", err)\n38: \t}\n39: \n40: \trsaPub, ok := pub.(*rsa.PublicKey)\n41: \tif !ok {\n42: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"public key is not RSA\")\n43: \t}\n44: \n45: \tam.mutex.Lock()\n46: \tam.publicKey = rsaPub\n47: \tam.mutex.Unlock()\n48: \n49: \treturn nil\n50: }\n51: \n52: func (am *AuthManager) AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc {\n53: \treturn func(c *gin.Context) {\n54: \t\tauthHeader := c.GetHeader(\"Authorization\")\n55: \t\tif authHeader == \"\" {\n56: \t\t\tc.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n57: \t\t\t\t\"error\":  \"Missing Authorization header\",\n58: \t\t\t\t\"code\":   http.StatusUnauthorized,\n59: \t\t\t\t\"detail\": \"JWT token required\",\n60: \t\t\t})\n61: \t\t\treturn\n62: \t\t}\n63: \n64: \t\tparts := strings.Split(authHeader, \" \")\n65: \t\tif len(parts) != 2 || parts[0] != \"Bearer\" {\n66: \t\t\tc.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n67: \t\t\t\t\"error\":  \"Invalid Authorization header format\",\n68: \t\t\t\t\"code\":   http.StatusUnauthorized,\n69: \t\t\t\t\"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\",\n70: \t\t\t})\n71: \t\t\treturn\n72: \t\t}\n73: \n74: \t\ttokenString := parts[1]\n75: \n76: \t\ttoken, err := jwt.Parse(tokenString, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n77: \t\t\tif _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA); !ok {\n78: \t\t\t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"unexpected signing method: %v\", token.Header[\"alg\"])\n79: \t\t\t}\n80: \t\t\tam.mutex.RLock()\n81: \t\t\tdefer am.mutex.RUnlock()\n82: \t\t\treturn am.publicKey, nil\n83: \t\t}, jwt.WithExpirationRequired(), jwt.WithIssuedAt(), jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute))\n84: \n85: \t\tif err != nil || !token.Valid {\n86: \t\t\tdetail := \"\"\n87: \t\t\tif err != nil {\n88: \t\t\t\tdetail = err.Error()\n89: \t\t\t}\n90: \t\t\tc.AbortWithStatusJSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n91: \t\t\t\t\"error\":  \"Invalid token\",\n92: \t\t\t\t\"code\":   http.StatusUnauthorized,\n93: \t\t\t\t\"detail\": detail,\n94: \t\t\t})\n95: \t\t\treturn\n96: \t\t}\n97: \n98: \t\tc.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)\n99: \t\tc.Next()\n100: \t}\n101: }\n102: \n103: func newAuthManager() *AuthManager {\n104: \treturn &AuthManager{}\n105: }\n106: \n107: func checkFatal(err error) {\n108: \tif err != nil {\n109: \t\tklog.Fatalf(\"failed to load public key: %v\", err)\n110: \t}\n111: }\n\n(End of file - total 111 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package picod\n\nimport (\n\t\"crypto/rsa\"\n\t\"crypto/x509\"\n\t\"encoding/pem\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"net/http\"\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"strings\"\n\t\"sync\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n\t\"github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\ntype AuthManager struct {\n\tpublicKey *rsa.PublicKey","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/auth.go","time":{"start":1775843593881,"end":1775843593887}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843594992,"sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","part":{"id":"prt_d7886cf24001PaSUGmvFoFyy3o","messageID":"msg_d7886a03a001nK7OtPxp2Df7BZ","sessionID":"ses_2877b9e1effesWMei9GCvRu7ve","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d3ac676d92d044f5a53c7851","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/server.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/server.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package picod\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"fmt\"\n5: \t\"net/http\"\n6: \t\"os\"\n7: \t\"path/filepath\"\n8: \t\"time\"\n9: \n10: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n11: \t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n12: )\n13: \n14: type Server struct {\n15: \tengine       *gin.Engine\n16: \tconfig       Config\n17: \tauthManager  *AuthManager\n18: \tstartTime    time.Time\n19: \tworkspaceDir string\n20: }\n21: \n22: func NewServer(config Config) *Server {\n23: \tgin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)\n24: \tengine := gin.New()\n25: \tengine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n26: \n27: \tauthManager := newAuthManager()\n28: \tif err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n29: \t\tcheckFatal(err)\n30: \t}\n31: \n32: \tworkspaceDir := config.Workspace\n33: \tif workspaceDir == \"\" {\n34: \t\tcwd, err := os.Getwd()\n35: \t\tif err != nil {\n36: \t\t\tklog.Fatalf(\"failed to get current working directory: %v\", err)\n37: \t\t}\n38: \t\tworkspaceDir = cwd\n39: \t} else {\n40: \t\tabsPath, err := filepath.Abs(workspaceDir)\n41: \t\tif err != nil {\n42: \t\t\tklog.Fatalf(\"failed to resolve workspace path: %v\", err)\n43: \t\t}\n44: \t\tworkspaceDir = absPath\n45: \t}\n46: \n47: \ts := &Server{\n48: \t\tengine:       engine,\n49: \t\tconfig:       config,\n50: \t\tauthManager:  authManager,\n51: \t\tstartTime:    time.Now(),\n52: \t\tworkspaceDir: workspaceDir,\n53: \t}\n54: \n55: \ts.registerRoutes()\n56: \n57: \treturn s\n58: }\n59: \n60: func (s *Server) registerRoutes() {\n61: \tapi := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")\n62: \tapi.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n63: \t{\n64: \t\tapi.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)\n65: \t\tapi.POST(\"/files\", s.UploadFileHandler)\n66: \t\tapi.GET(\"/files\", s.ListFilesHandler)\n67: \t\tapi.GET(\"/files/*path\", s.DownloadFileHandler)\n68: \t}\n69: \ts.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)\n70: }\n71: \n72: func (s *Server) Run() error {\n73: \tserver := &http.Server{\n74: \t\tAddr:              fmt.Sprintf(\":%d\", s.config.Port),\n75: \t\tHandler:           s.engine,\n76: \t\tReadHeaderTimeout: 10 * time.Second,\n77: \t}\n78: \treturn server.ListenAndServe()\n79: }\n80: \n81: func (s *Server) HealthCheckHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n82: \tc.JSON(http.StatusOK, gin.H{\n83: \t\t\"status\":  \"ok\",\n84: \t\t\"service\": \"PicoD\",\n85: \t\t\"version\": \"0.0.1\",\n86: \t\t\"uptime\":  time.Since(s.startTime).String(),\n87: \t})\n88: }\n\n(End of file - total 88 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package picod\n\nimport (\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"net/http\"\n\t\"os\"\n\t\"path/filepath\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n\t\"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n)\n\ntype Server struct {\n\tengine       *gin.Engine\n\tconfig       Config\n\tauthManager  *AuthManager\n\tstartTime    time.Time\n\tworkspaceDir string\n}","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/picod/server.go","time":{"start":1775843594985,"end":1775843594991}}}}
